Package edu.doane.dugal.samples.functions

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Ackley
    Sample DEA application to optimize Ackley's function, f_5 = - \left( 20 + e - 20^{-0.2 \sqrt{ \frac{1}{30} \sum_{i = i}^{30} x_i^2 }} - e^{ \frac{1}{30} \sum_{i = 1}^{30} \cos \left( 2 \pi x_i \right) } \right) where -30.0 \leq x_i \leq 30.0.
    BinaryDeJong01

    DeJong04
    Sample DEA application to optimize DeJong's fourth function, f_4 = -\left( \sum_{i = 1}^{30} \left( ix_i^4 + Gauss\left( 0, 1 \right) \right) \right), -1.28 \leq x_i \leq 1.28 (This is the negation of the standard DeJong's fourth function, since the DEA maximizes instead of minimizes.)
    Griewangk
    Sample DEA application to optimize Griewangk's function, f_6 = -1 - \sum_{i = 1}^{10} \left( \frac{x_i^2}{4000} \right) + \prod_{i = 1}^{10} \left( \cos \left( \frac{x_i}{\sqrt{i}} \right) \right) where -600 \leq x_i \leq 600.
    Rastrigin
    Sample DEA application to optimize Rastrigin's function, f_7 = -\left( 200 + \sum_{i = 1}^{20} \left( x_i^2 - 10 \cos \left( 2 \pi x_i \right) \right) \right), where -5.12 \leq x_i \leq 5.12.
    SchwefelSineRoot
    Sample DEA application to optimize Schwefel's Sine Root function, f_8 = -\left( 4189.829 + \sum_{i = 1}^{10} \left( -x_i \sin \left( \sqrt{ | x_i | } \right) \right) \right) where -500 \leq x_i \leq 500.
    ShekelsFoxHoles
    Sample DEA application to optimize Skekel's Foxholes function, f_9 = \sum_{i = 1}^m \left( \sum_{j = 1}^4 \left( x_j - C_{ij} \right)^2 + \Beta_i \right)^{-1}, where m = 10, and C and \Beta are as shown in the code.
